trans-unit.source: Makes a request to an entire <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref> or to a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref> in a package, identified by a pack URI.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IO.Packaging> [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_api#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-apisharpplural-md.md)] use a defined pack uri syntax to refer to parts that are contained in a package.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IO.Packaging>[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_api#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-apisharpplural-md.md)] använda en definierad pack uri-syntax för att referera till delar som ingår i ett paket.</xref:System.IO.Packaging>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Net.Cache.RequestCachePolicy"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The CachePolicy property is distinct from the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.CachePolicy%2A> of the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> returned by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> method.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the connection group.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger namnet på gruppen anslutning.

trans-unit.source: The ConnectionGroupName property enables the request to be associated with a connection group.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConnectionGroupName aktiverar begäran som ska associeras med en grupp.

trans-unit.source: A connection group is useful when application makes requests to the same server for different users.
trans-unit.target: En grupp är användbart när program som gör begäranden till samma server för olika användare.

trans-unit.source: The ConnectionGroupName property is an empty string if the request resolves from the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore> cache.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConnectionGroupName är en tom sträng om begäran löser från den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>cache.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>

trans-unit.source: The ConnectionGroupName property is shared with the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConnectionGroupName delas med inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>(<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The connection group name.
trans-unit.target: Gruppnamn för anslutningen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the `Content-length` [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_http](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-http-md.md)] header.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den `Content-length` [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_http](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-http-md.md)] huvud.

trans-unit.source: Note that the pack URI protocol does not process information in the request other than the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Observera att pack URI-protokollet inte bearbeta information i begäran än den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For most traditional purposes (such as estimating the size of POST information), there is no need for this property.
trans-unit.target: För de flesta traditionella (till exempel beräknar storlek på POST information) är behövs det ingen för den här egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: ContentLength returns 0 if the request resolves from the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore> cache.
trans-unit.target: ContentLength returnerar 0 om begäran matchar från den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>cache.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>

trans-unit.source: The ContentLength property is shared with the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ContentLength delas med inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>(<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The content length, in bytes.

trans-unit.source: Note that the pack URI protocol does not process information in the request other than the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Observera att pack URI-protokollet inte bearbeta information i begäran än den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For most purposes (such as determining the type of POST information), there is no use for this property.
trans-unit.target: Det finns ingen användning för den här egenskapen för de flesta ändamål (till exempel för att avgöra vilken typ av POST-information).

trans-unit.source: ContentType returns an empty string if the request resolves from the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore> cache.
trans-unit.target: ContentType returneras en tom sträng om begäran löser från den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>cache.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>

trans-unit.source: The contents of the header.
trans-unit.target: Innehållet i huvudet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the authentication credentials.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger autentiseringsuppgifter.

trans-unit.source: Requests to the package cache use their own cached credentials.
trans-unit.target: Begäranden till paketcachen använda sina egna cachelagrade autentiseringsuppgifter.

trans-unit.source: The Credentials property is shared with the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen autentiseringsuppgifter delas med inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>(<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The authentication credentials to use with the request.
trans-unit.target: Autentiseringsuppgifter som ska användas med begäran.

trans-unit.target: Hämtar inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The GetInnerRequest is provided for advanced scenarios only and is not needed for normal operation.
trans-unit.target: GetInnerRequest tillhandahålls för avancerade scenarier och behövs inte för normal drift.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> created from the inner-URI if the request resolves to a valid transport protocol such http or ftp; or a <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> created with a null-URI if the request resolves from the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore"></xref> cache.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>skapas från den inre-URI om begäran matchar till en giltig transport protokollet sådana http eller ftp, eller ett <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>skapas med en null-URI om begäran matchar från den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore"> </xref> cache.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The inner URI does not resolve to a valid transport protocol such as http for ftp, nor can the request be resolved from the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore"></xref>.

trans-unit.target: Returnerar svarsdataströmmen för begäran.

trans-unit.target: Per signaturen för basklassen returnerar GetResponse värde av typen <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the collection of header name/value pairs associated with the request.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger mängden huvudet namn/värde-par som är associerad med begäran.

trans-unit.source: Package cache requests include a valid but otherwise empty header collection in their requests.
trans-unit.target: Paketet cachebegäranden omfattar en giltig, men annars tom huvud-samlingen i begäranden.

trans-unit.source: The Headers property is shared with the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen huvuden delas med inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>(<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: A header collection object.
trans-unit.target: Ett huvud collection-objekt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the protocol method to use with the pack URI request.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger protocol-metod som ska användas med pack URI-begäran.

trans-unit.source: The Method property returns an empty string if the request resolves from the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore> cache.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen metoden returnerar en tom sträng om begäran löser från den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>cache.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>

trans-unit.source: The Method property is only set when request references an external Web request, such as http or ftp.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen metoden är endast anges när begäran refererar till en extern webbtjänst begäran, till exempel http eller ftp.

trans-unit.source: The Method property is shared with the inner <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen metoden delas med inre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>(<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The protocol method name that performs this request.
trans-unit.target: Protokollet metodnamnet som utför den här begäran.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether to preauthenticate the request.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om preauthenticate begäran.

trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] på den resurs som är kopplad till begäran.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the length of time before the request times out.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger hur lång tid innan tidsgränsen uppnås för begäran.

trans-unit.source: Requests to the package cache do not time out.
trans-unit.target: Begäranden till paketcachen saknar tidsgräns.

trans-unit.source: For requests that resolve from the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore> cache, Timeout returns a value of –1.
trans-unit.target: För begäranden från att matcha den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>cache, Timeout returnerar ett värde av –&1;.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageStore>

trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Timeout delas med inre begäran (<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest.GetInnerRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: The number of milliseconds to wait before the request times out.
trans-unit.target: Antalet millisekunder att vänta innan begäran på grund av timeout.
